com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.connectionLib

Class MessageVisitorAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.connectionLib.MessageVisitorAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMessageVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ErrorMessageVisitor, FieldBusEventProvider, SunriseControllerStateTrackerImpl

    public class MessageVisitorAdapter
extends Object
implements IMessageVisitor
    Default implementation for IMessageVisitor that ignores most messages and dispatches messages contained in a MessageType.LIST message to itself.

      • redispatchMessage

        protected void redispatchMessage(IMessageVisitor.Context context)
        Used to re-dispatch messages contained in a MessageType.LIST message. The default is to call Message.accept(IMessageVisitor) with this as visitor argument. Implementations may override this method to provide some other behavior.
        Parameters:
        context - An IMessageVisitor.Context for the operation.
